			<br>Pedersen, Holger. 1909–1913. <i>Vergleichende Grammatik des Keltischen</i>. 2 Vols. Göttingen: Vandenhoeck & Ruprecht.
			<br>Russell, Paul. 2008. What was best of every language: the early history of the Irish language. In Ó Cróinín, Dáibhí (ed.), <i>A New History of Ireland: Prehistoric and Early Ireland.</i> Vol 1. Oxford: Oxford University Press. 405‒450.
			<br>University College Cork: Department of Early and Medieval Irish. 2021. <a href=" https://www.ucc.ie/en/smg/cdi/" style="color:#0000FF;" target="_blank"> <i> Celtic Digital Initiative (CDI).</i> </a> University College Cork: Department of Early and Medieval Irish. (Accessed 2021-07-07.)
